name: Soy Sauce
description: This is naturally brewed soy sauce with whole soybeans, featuring a delicate aroma and mild flavour. As light Asian dressings and dipping sauces for vegetables and seafood, adding it changes daily diet to extraordinary-like magic.

name: Sukiyaki Sauce
description: This is a ready-to-use sukiyaki sauce produced by Kinryu Foods. This product lets you experience one of the most famous Japanese hot pots at home.

name: Dashi Stock Powder
description: If you're aiming for the delectable taste of seasonal vegetables, we recommend using vegetable soup stock. Free from onion, garlic, celery, carrots, cabbage, and raw animal ingredients.

name: Golden Curry
description: Golden Curry consists of curry powder, flour, spices, and seasonings that can quickly transform mundane stew into fine curry simply by adding them to the mixture.

name: Wasabi Paste
description: A ready-to-use Japanese horseradish paste packed in an easy-to-use plastic tube. Use this product to enjoy a contrast of sharp punch and delicate aroma of authentic Japanese wasabi.

name: Miso Paste
description: The miso is made with organic certified soybeans and rice harvested in Japan. It is fermented by a traditional barrel brewing for a whole year without heat sterilizing. This provides extra-rich flavour and a significant umami boost thanks to the enzymes.

name: Rich Butter Cream Sandwich Biscuits
description: The cracker-style biscuit is crisp and light, and the cream filling is enough to balance the flavour and texture perfectly. Vitamins such as calcium, vitamin D, vitamin B1, and vitamin B2 are also included in these sandwich biscuits, so they are great for growing children.

name: Calbee Potato Chips
description: Calbee Potato Chips is the renowned and top-selling Japanese potato chip, commanding about 70% of the potato chips market share in Japan. Seasoned with salt and two types of seaweed, these thinly sliced chips boast a crispy texture and a delicate mouthfeel.

name: Gion Tsuji Toshi Kyoto Matcha Confectionery
description: Giono-no-Sato is a renowned matcha confectionery from Gion Tsuji, a long-standing and well-known brand. It features a delicate roasted rice cracker, wrapped in a sweet white cream, and infused with vibrant green matcha.

name: ROYCE Potato Chips
description: The refined caramel flavor intertwines with the fragrance of potato chips. The chips, perfectly crisp on one side, enhance the caramel notes of white chocolate.

name: Assorted Rice Crackers
description: This rice cracker boasts a melt-in-the-mouth texture, eliminating the need for chewing. Its gentle nature on the stomach makes it suitable for babies starting on solid foods. Utilizing 100% domestic ingredients.

name: Chocolate Pocky Biscuit Sticks
description: Pocky stands out as the most popular and renowned Japanese sweet snack, and for good reason! Each Giant Pocky pack contains eight regular-sized packages of Pockys featuring biscuit sticks coated in delicious chocolate-flavoured frosting.

name: Tonkotsu Ramen
description: This Ramen features a soup base crafted from pork bone extract, resulting in a rich and cloudy broth infused with a blend of vegetables and spices.

name: Curry Noodle
description: This Curry Flavored Nissin Cup Noodle is BIG! Curry soup has the mild, sweet taste of vegetables, and thick noodles taste richly.

name: Spinach and Bacon Soup
description: This is a hearty egg soup brimming with ingredients such as spinach and bacon. Made with spinach sourced from a designated farm and eggs collected within three days from a domestic contracted poultry farm.

name: Miso Soup
description: A fusion of two rice miso varieties, featuring the budget-friendly raw miso type.

name: Cheese Pasta Sauce
description: Celebrating its 25th anniversary since its 2020 launch, the Blue Cave Series blends black pepper and Parmesan cheese, featuring blue cheese, Pecorino Romano.

name: Nissin Yakisoba
description: An enticing appetite meets the deliciousness of the fragrant dense sauce! Essential ingredients include cabbage and pork infused with blue glue and red ginger.

name: Premium Japanese Green Tea
description: Indulge in the harmonious fusion of traditional Japanese green tea and Uji Matcha with our Premium Tea Bags Japanese Green Tea with Uji Matcha!

name: Matcha Latte
description: Matcha Milk Tea Latte is made from pure Japanese matcha green tea powder, sourced from fresh tea leaves harvested from the Hokkaido mountains in a new, clean, and safe natural environment.

name: Honey Lemon Squash
description: Enjoy a light and invigorating carbonated beverage crafted with two distinct lemon ingredients enhanced by the addition of honey. Delight in the distinctive gentle sweetness of honey.

name: Sakura Latte
description: Relax and make yourself a nice cup of warm or cold sakura-flavoured latte! Each cup of latte you make blends the flavour of cherries and mellow milk.

name: Prestigious Junmai Daiginjo Sake
description: Indulge in this opulent set, a sip beyond the pinnacle of sake, Junmai Daiginjo! Crafted under the expert supervision of a master sake brewer, it offers a truly luxurious experience.

name: Wild Blueberry Infused Black Vinegar
description: Delicious and easy to drink, you can easily get black vinegar daily. Incorporates elusive wild blueberries and utilizes locally sourced black rice vinegar without any added sweetness.

name: Barley Grass Juice
description: This Barely Grass Juice is made of 100% pure organically grown green barley young leaves. The leaves are carefully processed into powder and they are naturally rich in minerals, vitamins, and fibres.

name: Gummy Drops with Cod Liver Oil and Probiotics
description: Making vitamin intake enjoyable for kids (or adults!) has never been simpler! These banana-flavored gummies are packed with vitamins A, B2, B6, D, and liver oil.

name: Placenta Collagen Jelly
description: BEAUPOWER Placenta Collagen offers a potent blend with 60,000mg of placenta, 40,000mg of isoflavones in collagen, and a rich infusion of 75 fermented plant extracts per box.

name: Aged Black Garlic Supplement
description: If you're facing morning fatigue and a lack of energy, consider the remedy found in aged black garlic. Created using a patented method in Aomori Prefecture, this garlic variation promotes endurance and fortitude.

name: Daily Essential Vitamins Juice
description: Containing 13 vitamins aligned with Reference Values, this product is devoid of artificial sweeteners. Infused with a zesty, sweet orange taste, it incorporates orange and mandarin juice for added refreshment.

name: Brewer's Yeast Powder
description: Elevate your daily meals with the nutritional benefits of Brewer's Yeast Powder. This dietary supplement seamlessly blends into common dishes such as curry, hamburgers, or fried chicken coatings, enriching them with its unique formulation.
